<div type="letter" id="z0385">
<lg type="poem">
<l>Quam Christianam, Christiane, gratiam</l>
<l>Patri rependis! qui semel vitam tibi</l>
<l>Casu caducam contulit, fluxam, brevem,</l>
<l>Huic arte longam prorogas et perpetem,</l>
<l>Et alterum sic te Patris praestas Patrem.<note n="#1"/></l>
</lg>
<div type="closer">
<p><date>14 Apr. 1657</date>.</p>
